name: Harvest Diversified Equity Income ETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks to provide holders of Class A Units with high monthly cash distributions and the opportunity for capital appreciation. The fund investing on a non-levered basis, in a portfolio of exchange traded mutual funds managed by the Manager that are listed on a recognized Canadian stock exchange and that engage in covered call strategies.
